text: Haut-Katanga is one of the 26 provinces of the Democratic Republic of the Congo. The capital is Lubumbashi. Before 2015 it was part of the Katanga Province. Its territories are: * Kasenga * Kipushi * Mitwaba * Pweto * Sakania ==References== Category:Provinces of the Democratic Republic of the Congo Category:2015 establishments in Africa
title: Haut-Katanga Province
